00:28:15.780 --> 00:28:17.200
and sit and meditate.

00:28:17.200 --> 00:28:19.860
So there's that.

00:28:19.860 --> 00:28:22.640
But as you said,
what about that gap?

00:28:22.640 --> 00:28:27.650
So I don't think you need to
have your work groups also

00:28:27.650 --> 00:28:29.480
be your meditation groups.

00:28:29.480 --> 00:28:32.640
I think those who are interested
could find each other.

00:28:32.640 --> 00:28:36.950
I bet you have
technology for this--

00:28:36.950 --> 00:28:39.590
where those who are interested
could find each other.

00:28:39.590 --> 00:28:44.400
And I think a good size is,
like, six to eight people.

00:28:44.400 --> 00:28:48.180
And if it's more than that there
could be more groups, you know?

00:28:48.180 --> 00:28:49.430
There could be lots of groups.

00:28:49.430 --> 00:28:51.763
I don't know how many people
you have working at Google,

00:28:51.763 --> 00:28:54.210
but there could be many,
many of these groups.

00:28:54.210 --> 00:28:57.680
And they can sit in somebody's
office or a little nook

00:28:57.680 --> 00:29:01.650
in the cafeteria, whatever.

00:29:01.650 --> 00:29:05.750
And just decide, you
know, one a week,

00:29:05.750 --> 00:29:07.750
Wednesdays for
lunch or after work

00:29:07.750 --> 00:29:11.010
