00:29:16.650 --> 00:29:19.140
We have an online course and
they're weekly installments,

00:29:19.140 --> 00:29:21.910
and so people could
do that together,

00:29:21.910 --> 00:29:23.720
which would be really fun.

00:29:23.720 --> 00:29:27.050
Or work their way through
the book, or both because,

00:29:27.050 --> 00:29:29.910
not surprisingly,
since I designed both,

00:29:29.910 --> 00:29:32.750
they're very similar.

00:29:32.750 --> 00:29:34.670
Basically covering
