00:29:34.670 --> 00:29:36.580
But the book gives
you more background.

00:29:36.580 --> 00:29:39.500
It's got more richness to it.

00:29:39.500 --> 00:29:43.240
And so it's a good thing to
refer to at least on your own.

00:29:43.240 --> 00:29:49.470
And if you guys do set
up learning circles,

00:29:49.470 --> 00:29:51.990
at least for the next little
while every time I come back

00:29:51.990 --> 00:29:56.510
to California what I'd like to
