00:29:56.510 --> 00:29:59.920
and talk with people about,
what's your experience?

00:29:59.920 --> 00:30:01.240
How is it going on the cushion?

00:30:01.240 --> 00:30:02.448
How is it going in the group?

00:30:02.448 --> 00:30:04.700
And that kind of thing.

00:30:04.700 --> 00:30:09.990
The other thing is, I have
