and what's inside the water.

00:32:57.417 --> 00:32:58.750
But what if that doesn't happen?

00:33:01.580 --> 00:33:03.580
LAMA TSOMO: Well, I thought
it wasn't happening.

00:33:03.580 --> 00:33:05.440
