00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:08.200
And it was only in retrospect
that I realized, wait a minute,

00:33:08.200 --> 00:33:11.200
it was happening more
than I thought it was.

00:33:11.200 --> 00:33:14.010
I think we Westerners have kind
of a low opinion of ourselves,

00:33:14.010 --> 00:33:17.720
and it's rather unjustified.

00:33:17.720 --> 00:33:20.460
At one point it kind
have occurred to me--

00:33:20.460 --> 00:33:22.310
and this is before
my Buddhist days--

00:33:22.310 --> 00:33:26.980
