is made of God, then so

00:33:26.980 --> 00:33:30.330
is everybody, including me.

00:33:30.330 --> 00:33:31.830
So that's what we're
really made of,

00:33:31.830 --> 00:33:34.288
is something that's very pure,
whatever we want to call it.

00:33:34.288 --> 00:33:38.370
You know, whatever that source
is, that's our source, too.

00:33:38.370 --> 00:33:40.680
And so maybe we're not
so terrible after all.

00:33:40.680 --> 00:33:46.970
But there's a funny story I love
to tell about Mingyur Rinpoche.

00:33:46.970 --> 00:33:52.920
He's another Lama who-- the
Lamas coming from the East

00:33:52.920 --> 00:33:55.980
were confused by
this Western penchant

00:33:55.980 --> 00:33:58.140
for kicking ourselves and
thinking we're terrible

00:33:58.140 --> 00:34:00.910
and, "I'm not worthy"
and this kind of thing.

00:34:00.910 --> 00:34:02.740
Having no compassion
or love for ourselves.

00:34:02.740 --> 00:34:05.920
And then, what basis
then do we have

00:34:05.920 --> 00:34:09.159
for having compassion and
love for everybody else?

00:34:09.159 --> 00:34:12.380
Love thy neighbor as thyself,
even is in the Bible.

00:34:12.380 --> 00:34:16.710
So then maybe that's
why America falls

00:34:16.710 --> 00:34:20.840
so short of our aspirations to
be a compassionate and loving

00:34:20.840 --> 00:34:22.550
country.

00:34:22.550 --> 00:34:25.420
But anyway, Mingyur
Rinpoche really

00:34:25.420 --> 00:34:28.210
was trying to understand
his American students,

00:34:28.210 --> 00:34:32.340
and he finally decided to do
this unworthiness meditation.

00:34:32.340 --> 00:34:34.679
And so he practiced
it every day.

00:34:34.679 --> 00:34:37.480
And eventually, after
a couple of weeks

00:34:37.480 --> 00:34:42.699
of assiduously practicing this,
he was feeling kind of crummy.

00:34:42.699 --> 00:34:44.949
And it just got kind
of worse and worse

00:34:44.949 --> 00:34:47.570
and then he finally
realized one day,

00:34:47.570 --> 00:34:49.469
I feel terrible about myself.

00:34:49.469 --> 00:34:51.350
Isn't this great?

00:34:51.350 --> 00:34:54.350
Now I understand my
Western students.

00:34:54.350 --> 00:34:55.780
He was so happy.

00:34:55.780 --> 00:34:58.950
And of course, he was able to
reverse it with the practices

00:34:58.950 --> 00:35:04.500
that he knew and was able
to really help his students.

00:35:04.500 --> 00:35:07.420
FEMALE SPEAKER: I have one
